This software includes code from the Piskel project:
https://github.com/piskelapp/piskel

Piskel is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
Copyright (c) 2013 Julian Descottes

Makapix Club integrates Piskel as a pixel art editor, with modifications
to enable seamless publishing of artwork to the Makapix platform. The 
integration includes:
- Custom export functionality to publish directly to Makapix
- Modified UI to include Makapix-specific buttons and workflows
- Integration layer for communication between Piskel and Makapix
- Deployment configuration for hosting as part of the Makapix service

The original Piskel source code and license can be found at:
https://github.com/piskelapp/piskel

================================================================================

